%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20took%20my%20first%20solo%20trip%20to%20Iceland.%20It%20didn't%20transform%20me%2C%20but%20it%20did%20wonders%20for%20my%20anxiety%20levels%20and%20confidence.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20smiling%20in%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995d94ba645d1188189811f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20built%20my%20confidence%20and%20worked%20on%20my%20anxiety%20while%20traveling%20alone%20on%20my%20first%20solo%20trip.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20years%2C%20I've%20struggled%20with%20anxiety%2C%20and%20it%20has%20held%20me%20back%20from%20pursuing%20solo%20travel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAround%20my%2030th%20birthday%2C%20I%20worked%20up%20the%20courage%20to%20book%20a%20trip%20to%20Iceland%20by%20myself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20adventure%20helped%20me%20overcome%20many%20of%20my%20anxieties%20and%20gain%20the%20confidence%20to%20solo%20travel%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20drove%20through%20Iceland's%20dramatic%20landscape%20alone%20this%20past%20June%2C%20listening%20to%20Bon%20Iver's%20%26quot%3BHolocene%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20started%20to%20cry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20crying%20in%20sheer%20awe%20at%20my%20surroundings%20and%20the%20lyrics%20of%20a%20favorite%20song%2C%20one%20about%20a%20man%20pondering%20his%20significance.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20though%2C%20I%20was%20crying%20because%20I%20was%20proud%20of%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20faced%20a%20fear%20of%20mine%20head-on%2C%20and%20it%20brought%20me%20to%20an%20emotional%2C%20yet%20blissful%20moment%20that%20I'll%20never%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-trip-to-japan-mistakes-lessons-american-solo-traveler-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20solo%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20me%20that%20what%20I%20perceived%20as%20a%20threat%20wasn't%20really%20one%20after%20all%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20continue%20traveling%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a618953-9eeb-4922-ba84-bfd7f6e437f6%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20my%20anxiety%20holding%20me%20back%2C%20I%20planned%20a%20solo%20trip%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20of%20waterfall%20on%20green%20mountains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995d83ef8731049f3af4f59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22941%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20solo%20travel%20didn't%20feel%20like%20an%20option.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20rewind%20a%20bit%2C%20I've%20always%20been%20an%20anxious%20person%2C%20but%20it%20really%20manifested%20in%20my%20mid-20s%20when%20I%20started%20listening%20to%20true-crime%20podcasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuge%20mistake.%20I%20know%20too%20much%20now%20about%20what%20horrific%20acts%20people%20are%20capable%20of.%20My%20mind%20would%20conjure%20scenarios%20in%20which%20something%20I'd%20just%20listened%20to%20could%20happen%20to%20me%20or%20a%20loved%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20started%20to%20impact%20my%20life%20in%20different%20ways%20%E2%80%94%20if%20my%20boyfriend%20was%20on%20a%20work%20trip%2C%20I%20was%20scared%20to%20leave%20our%20apartment.%20When%20my%20mom%20moved%20into%20her%20new%20home%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20have%20an%20alarm%20system%20set%20up%2C%20I%20insisted%20I%20couldn't%20stay%20the%20night%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20had%20a%20tight%20grip%20on%20me%20at%20home%2C%20so%20the%20thought%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-travel-used-to-be-fun-older-now-not-interested-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esolo%20traveling%20by%20myself%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Absolutely%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lavendar%20field%20with%20hills%20in%20distance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995d83ea645d118818980fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22865%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20I%20began%20researching%20where%20to%20go%2C%20Iceland%20often%20came%20up.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20last%20January%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20freshly%20laid%20off%2C%20about%20to%20turn%2030%20in%20six%20months%2C%20with%20a%20long%20list%20of%20places%20I%20wanted%20to%20travel%20to%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20what%20changed%20in%20me%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20it%20was%20hitting%20a%20milestone%20age%20%E2%80%94%20but%20after%20many%20internal%20battles%2C%20I%20decided%20I'd%20visit%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%20solo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20settled%20on%20Iceland%2C%20which%20is%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafest-countries-in-world-for-expats-living-abroad-ranking-work-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esafest%20countries%20in%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20made%20following%20through%20on%20my%20decision%20a%20bit%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20told%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20my%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20even%20my%20esthetician%E2%80%94%20about%20my%20travel%20plans%20because%20the%20more%20people%20who%20knew%2C%20the%20harder%20it%20would%20be%20for%20me%20to%20back%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20I%20rented%20a%20campervan%20for%20three%20days%2C%20with%20a%20plan%20to%20explore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ficeland-road-trip-experience-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIceland's%20Ring%20Road%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a1de95ab-3438-4f1b-9efd-0278a873717a%5C%22%3EThis%20trip%20didn't%20entirely%20change%20me%2C%20but%20it%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20keep%20solo%20traveling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20with%20arms%20up%20in%20front%20of%20car%20in%20Iceland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995d7ffe1ba468a96ac3876%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeemingly%20small%20experiences%20on%20my%20trip%20helped%20me%20build%20confidence%20and%20overcome%20anxiety.%3Cp%3ELily%20Voss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENo%2C%20I%20didn't%20return%20from%20Iceland%20as%20an%20entirely%20different%20person%2C%20nor%20did%20I%20have%20a%20transformative%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-eat-pray-love-author-liz-gilbert-survived-her-success-2014-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEat%2C%20Pray%2C%20Love%26quot%3B%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20changed%20the%20fabric%20of%20who%20I%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%2C%20I%20found%20that%20seemingly%20small%20experiences%20on%20my%20trip%20helped%20me%20build%20confidence%20and%20overcome%20so%20much%20of%20the%20anxiety%20I'd%20been%20struggling%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20go%20on%20my%20first%20hike%20alone%20and%20actually%20enjoy%20myself.%20I%20drove%20in%20Iceland's%20notoriously%20high%20winds%20solo%2C%20staying%20calm%20as%20they%20shook%20my%20van.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20just%20being%20able%20to%20sleep%20(soundly%2C%20I%20might%20add)%20in%20my%20van%20at%20campsites%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20imagined%20happening%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20made%20me%20feel%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftricks-to-overcome-anxiety-and-fear-2014-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFacing%20my%20fears%3C%2Fa%3E%20head-on%20may%20have%20even%20rewired%20my%20brain%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20three-day%20adventure%2C%20I%20booked%20another%20solo%20trip%20to%20Annecy%2C%20France%2C%20later%20that%20summer.%20I'm%20still%20looking%20forward%20to%20going%20on%20even%20more%20adventures%20by%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20my%20anxiety%20still%20there%3F%20Definitely.%20However%2C%20taking%20that%20trip%20did%20help%20me%20deal%20with%20it%20in%20a%20healthier%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%2C%20facing%20this%20fear%20taught%20me%20that%20seeing%20what's%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20my%20worries%20might%20actually%20lead%20me%20to%20some%20of%20life's%20best%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-solo-trip-helped-feel-less-anxious-lessons-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771683481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995d94ba645d1188189811f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-solo-trip-helped-feel-less-anxious-lessons-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anxiety%20held%20me%20back%20from%20traveling%20alone%20for%20years%2C%20but%20I%20finally%20faced%20my%20fears%20with%20my%20first%20solo%20trip%20to%20Iceland.%20It%20helped%20build%20my%20confidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Lily%20Voss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-solo-trip-helped-feel-less-anxious-lessons-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Gupta%20calls%20Dhurandhar%202-Toxic%20BO%20clash%20'unfortunate'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771682892000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128646982%2Cimgsize-31360.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsanjay-gupta-calls-ranveer-singhs-dhurandhar-2-and-yashs-toxic-box-office-clash-unfortunate-both-films-will-do-well-but-neither-will-%2Farticleshow%2F128646854.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22http