rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20CBS%20News%2C%20Nanos%20described%20the%20backpack%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20promising%20leads%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheriff%20said%20investigators%20have%20been%20scouring%20surveillance%20footage%20from%20local%20Walmart%20stores%20and%20that%20the%20megaretailer%20has%20turned%20over%20records%20of%20all%20Ozark%20Trail%20Hiker%20backpack%20purchases%20from%20the%20last%20several%20months%2C%20the%20news%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Walmart%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22936%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Video%20image%20of%20a%20person%20of%20interest%20in%20Nancy%20Guthrie%20disappearance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69986ccba645d1188189a934%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22702%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FBI%20released%20this%20image%20related%20to%20the%20disappearance%20of%20Nancy%20Guthrie.%3Cp%3EFBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20only%20item%20that%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bpositively%20identified%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20suspect%20in%20the%20doorbell%20camera%20footage%20is%20the%20Ozark%20Trail%20Hiker%20packpack%2C%20a%20Pima%20County%20Sheriff's%20Department%20spokeswoman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestigators%20are%20working%20to%20determine%20where%20the%20other%20items%20may%20have%20been%20purchased%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokeswoman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENancy%20Guthrie's%20disappearance%20has%20gripped%20the%20nation.%20Her%20famous%20daughter%2C%20Savannah%20Guthrie%2C%20has%20issued%20tearful%20video%20messages%2C%20pleading%20for%20her%20mother's%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20not%20publicly%20identified%20any%20suspects%20or%20persons%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDNA%20found%20at%20Nancy%20Guthrie's%20property%20is%20being%20anal