2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Farshad-warsi-reveals-why-he-said-yes-to-shah-rukh-khans-king-and-aryans-the-bads-of-bollywood%2Farticleshow%2F128644626.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F128644626.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EArshad%20Warsi%20recently%20opened%20up%20about%20his%20involvement%20in%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20upcoming%20film%20'King'%20and%20Aryan%20Khan's%20directorial%20debut%2C%20'The%20Ba***ds%20of%20Bollywood.'%20He%20emphasized%20that%20his%20commitment%20was%20fueled%20by%20his%20long-standing%20relationship%20with%20the%20Khan%20family%20rather%20than%20the%20allure%20of%20the%20screenplay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20military%20families%20are%20stuck%20on%20childcare%20waitlists.%20More%20spots%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20fix%20the%20deeper%20problems.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224826%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20childcare%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998ab94156648bc16a89cb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20military%20childcare%20development%20centers%20support%20service%20members%20and%20their%20families.%20There%20are%2C%20however%2C%20thousands%20of%20children%20waiting%20for%20spots%20to%20open%20up.%3Cp%3EAirman%20Paden%20Henry%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAround%207%2C800%20military%20children%20are%20waitlisted%20for%20childcare%2C%20according%20to%20congressional%20estimates.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAdvocates%20say%20the%20real%20number%20may%20be%20higher.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStaff%20shortages%20and%20high%20attrition%20are%20persistent%20problems%20for%20military%20childcare%20facilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20an%20estimated%207%2C800%20children%20on%20US%20military%20childcare%20waitlists.%20Military%20families%20and%20advocates%20say%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20number%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emasks%20deeper%20shortfalls%20that%20continue%20to%20sideline%20working%20spouses%20and%20strain%20service%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20raised%20the%20issue%20during%20a%20recent%20congressional%20hearing%2C%20calling%20the%20persistent%20backlog%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawmakers-push-to-prevent-barracks-funds-from-supporting-domestic-operations-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equality-of-life%3C%2Fa%3E%20problem%2C%20even%20as%20the%20waitlist%20has%20notably%20dropped%20from%2012%2C000%20children%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocates%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20number%20isn't%20the%20whole%20picture%20and%20excludes%20families%20who've%20given%20up%20out%20of%20frustration%20or%20can't%20use%20base%20centers%20that%20lack%20evening%2C%20weekend%2C%20or%20specialized%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20say%20that%20we%20are%20a%20military%20that%20cares%20about%20our%20families%20if%20we%20pretend%20to%20provide%20childcare%20and%20then%20we've%20got%20a%20waitlist%20that's%20got%207%2C800%20babies%20waiting%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Massachusetts%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20said%20to%20service%20senior%20enlisted%20leaders%20during%20last%20week's%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20service%20leaders%20present%20disputed%20that%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaster%20Chief%20Petty%20Officer%20of%20the%20Navy%20John%20Perryman%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20Navy%20still%20has%20roughly%201%2C400%20children%20in%20unmet%20need%20status%2C%20while%20Chief%20Master%20Sergeant%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%20David%20Wolfe%20said%20his%20service's%20waitlist%20stands%20at%20around%202%2C700%2C%20though%20there%20are%20efforts%20underway%20to%20open%20new%20spots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20how%20the%20remaining%20waitlisted%20children%20are%20divided%20between%20other%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20had%2095%2C000%20children%20under%205%20but%20space%20for%20only%20about%2023%2C000%20in%20its%20child%20development%20centers%2C%20a%202023%20service%20report%20on%20childcare%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Air%20Force%20spokesperson%20attributed%20that%20disparity%20to%20the%20number%20of%20children%20entering%20and%20leaving%20care%20throughout%20the%20year.%20%26quot%3BThe%20annual%20number%20served%20will%20not%20correlate%20with%20daily%20capacity%20and%20can%20be%20significantly%20higher%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20families%20require%20on-base%20care.%20But%20the%20report%20added%20that%20more%20facility%20construction%20alone%20would%20not%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bviable%20solution%20to%20meet%20all%20potential%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKayla%20Corbitt%2C%20a%20military%20spouse%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20a%20nonprofit%20dedicated%20to%20helping%20military%20families%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-family-spent-savings-on-expensive-childcare-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efind%20reliable%20childcare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20many%20families%20lose%20hope%20amid%20long%20waits.%20Staying%20on%20the%20waitlist%2C%20she%20said%2C%20requires%20logging%20on%20every%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20reconfirm%20before%20families%20are%20automatically%20disenrolled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20some%20families%2C%20the%20barriers%20extend%20beyond%20backlogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223808%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20room%20at%20the%20CDC%20at%20Ramstein%20Air%20Base%2C%20Germany%2C%20Jan.%2014%2C%202026.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998ac4f2237a6a8f0cd8df0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222539%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20room%20at%20the%20CDC%20at%20Ramstein%20Air%20Base%2C%20Germany%2C%20Jan.%2014%2C%202026.%3Cp%3EAirman%20Paden%20Henry%2FUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20needing%20evening%20care%2C%20weekend%20care%2C%20shift%20work%20care%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20military%2C%20they%20aren't%20going%20to%20try%20to%20get%20on%20that%20waitlist%2C%26quot%3B%20Corbitt%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20most%20child%20development%20centers%2C%20or%20CDCs%2C%20on%20bases%20don't%20offer%20late%20evening%20or%20very%20early%20morning%20care%20needed%20for%20troops%20on%2024-hour%20duty%20or%20for%20deployed%20service%20members%20with%20spouses%20who%20work%20unusual%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20children%20with%20special%20needs%20face%20significant%20obstacles%20in%20finding%20care%2C%20Corbitt%20said%2C%20as%20many%20CDCs%20are%20not%20equipped%20to%20provide%20care%2C%20and%20the%20policies%20sometimes%20vary%20from%20facility%20to%20facility%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20families%20to%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20when%20they%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrigit%20Schneider%2C%20an%20Air%20Force%20spouse%20and%20mother%20of%20three%20children%2C%20wants%20to%20return%20to%20work%20as%20a%20financial%20planner%20to%20better%20support%20her%20family%2C%20but%20because%20her%20local%20childcare%20center%20won't%20accept%20children%20with%20feeding%20tubes%2C%20one%20of%20her%20young%20children%20is%20shut%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20special%20needs%20mom%20perspective%2C%20it's%20an%20extra%20layer%20of%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchneider%20pays%20nearly%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20for%20one%20child%20to%20receive%20on-base%20childcare%2C%20another%20child%20is%20receiving%20private%20care%20due%20to%20the%20severity%20of%20their%20disability%2C%20and%20a%20third%20is%20at%20home.%20Schneider%20says%20the%20third%20should%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20base%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20G-tube%20really%20is%20not%20a%20hard%20medical%20device%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20use%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20though%2C%20military%20CDCs%20won't%20accept%20children%20with%20gastrostomy%20tubes.%20Facilities%20are%20often%20unable%2C%20or%20unwilling%2C%20to%20provide%20higher%20levels%20of%20care%2C%20Corbitt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAir%20Force%20childcare%20programs%20are%20%26quot%3Bsupported%20by%20a%20multidisciplinary%20team%20of%20experts%20who%20provide%20consultation%20and%20support%20to%20ensure%20the%20highest%20quality%20of%20inclusive%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Air%20Force%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20following%20a%20query%20regarding%20the%20service's%20childcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20%26quot%3Boffers%20a%20network%20of%20on-%20and%20off-installation%20care%20options%20and%20works%20closely%20with%20families%20to%20identify%20the%20appropriate%20setting%20for%20their%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20spokesperson%2C%20adding%20that%20waitlist%20data%20helps%20inform%20future%20allocation%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaffing%20shortages%20are%20another%20obstacle%20to%20reliable%20access%20for%20military%20personnel.%20Military%20childcare%20workers%20face%20unusually%20high%20attrition%20rates%2C%20around%2050%25%2C%20Warren%20said%20at%20last%20week's%20congressional%20hearing%2C%20driven%20largely%20by%20meager%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompounding%20the%20issue%20is%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20clear%20pathway%20that%20would%20allow%20qualified%20providers%20to%20move%20easily%20between%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2040%25%20of%20childcare%20workers%20are%20military%20spouses%2C%20said%20the%20Marine%20Corps'%20top%20enlisted%20leader%2C%20Sergeant%20Major%20Carlos%20Ruiz%2C%20during%20the%20hearing.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20just%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20smart%20about%20transferring%20folks%20and%20directly%20hiring%20from%20one%20CDC%20to%20another%2C%20we%20can%20reduce%20the%20attrition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20watchdogs%20have%20repeatedly%20flagged%20childcare%20accessibility%20as%20a%20point%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20US%20military.%20A%202024%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20report%20found%20that%20while%20the%20services%20focus%20heavily%20on%20recruiting%20new%20childcare%20workers%2C%20they%20do%20not%20consistently%20measure%20whether%20employee%20retention%20efforts%20are%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20military's%20childcare%20shortages%20aren't%20unique%20to%20the%20armed%20forces.%20Many%20Americans%20in%20the%20civilian%20world%20struggle%20to%20find%20reliable%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchildcare-too-expensive-unaffordable-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereasonably%20priced%20childcare%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-paid-over-fifty-thousand-dollars-for-childcare-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyear%20of%20childcare%3C%2Fa%3E%20amounts%20to%20an%20entire%20average%20salary%2C%20costing%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%20The%20cost%20of%20childcare%20in%20the%20US%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20150%25%20over%20the%20last%20quarter-century%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-expensive-daycare-childcare-inflation-working-parents-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtinues%20to%20climb%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20often%20outpacing%20inflation.%20In%20some%20areas%2C%20childcare%20costs%20can%20exceed%20rent%20or%20mortgage%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilitary-kids-are-still-waiting-for-childcare-spots-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insi