0Mountains%2C%20her%20rescue%20dog%20frolicking%20in%20her%20yard%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-of-4-downsized-house-to-save-money-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20small%20house%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20looks%20almost%20identical%20to%20hers%20just%20a%20few%20feet%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo%20doesn't%20live%20in%20a%20planned%20community%20with%20cookie-cutter%20homes%2C%20though.%20She%20lives%20in%20an%20accessory%20dwelling%20unit%2C%20or%20ADU%2C%20on%20her%20parents'%20land%2C%20sharing%20property%20and%20resources%20to%20save%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20one%20of%20thousands%20of%20Americans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-people-build-adus-housing-cost-benefits-cheaper-than-moving-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eturning%20to%20ADUs%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20more%20affordable%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMia%20Corippo%20has%20learned%20a%20lot%20about%20real%20estate%20and%20saving%20money%20from%20her%20parents%20over%20the%20years.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20with%20a%20coffee%20in%20front%20of%20a%20mountain%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f5553a645d11881894f3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223017%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20Corippo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo%2C%2026%2C%20grew%20up%20just%20outside%20Yosemite%20with%20her%20tight-knit%20family.%20The%20teacher%2C%20coach%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmia_corippo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtent%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E%20lived%20in%20Orange%20County%20for%20a%20few%20years%20for%20college%2C%20but%20she%20moved%20back%20in%20with%20her%20parents%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20have%20always%20been%20really%20big%20on%20us%20living%20with%20them%20and%20saving%20up%20money%20for%20as%20long%20as%20we%20can%2C%26quot%3B%20Corippo%20said%20of%20why%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-turned-garage-into-rent-free-apartment-for-son-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elived%20with%20her%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20her%20brother%20did%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20living%20with%20them%20when%20we%20came%20back%20from%20college%20and%20building%20our%20savings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo%20said%20her%20parents%20also%20instilled%20in%20her%20lessons%20about%20how%20real%20estate%20can%20set%20you%20up%20for%20financial%20success.%20When%20she%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20they%20turned%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20garage%20into%20an%20Airbnb.%20They%20let%20Corippo%20and%20her%20sister%20handle%20the%20housekeeping%20for%20the%20unit%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20their%20club%20volleyball%2C%20teaching%20her%20early%20that%20real%20estate%20could%20be%20a%20valuable%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20late%202023%2C%20her%20family%20took%20those%20lessons%20and%20built%20a%20small%20home%20on%20property%20near%20Yosemite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20camo%20hat%20smiles%20at%20something%20off%20to%20the%20right%20of%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f7c30e1ba468a96ac0e05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222225%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20Corippo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo's%20parents%20had%20purchased%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20land%20near%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyosemite-national-park-photos-government-shutdown-california-tourism-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enational%20park%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20California%20when%20real%20estate%20prices%20were%20low%2C%20unsure%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20started%20toying%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20a%20cabin%20on%20the%20land%2C%20Corippo%2C%20her%20brother%2C%20and%20her%20sister%20decided%20to%20pool%20their%20resources%20and%20invest%20in%20the%20build%20with%20her%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20were%20little%2C%20my%20parents%20invested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-faces-ftc-scrutiny-apple-news-content-curation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20they%20bought%20for%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Corippo%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20used%20those%20Apple%20stocks%20in%20our%20savings%20to%20invest%20in%20this%20first%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20650-square-foot%20house%20became%20a%20family%20project.%20It%20had%20one%20bedroom%2C%20a%20separate%20lofted%20sleeping%20area%2C%20and%20one%20bathroom.%20Corippo%20and%20her%20father%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20build%20cost%20around%20%24300%2C000%2C%20which%20included%20creating%20a%20well%2C%20septic%20tank%2C%20and%20driveway%20on%20the%20property.%20Corippo%20moved%20into%20the%20finished%20space%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20definitely%20a%20family%20collaboration%20of%20making%20it%20somewhere%20I%20could%20live%2C%20but%20also%20something%20that%20would%20be%20an%20investment%20once%20I%20moved%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Corippo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%2C%20Corippo%20decided%20she%20wanted%20a%20house%20for%20herself%20on%20their%20land.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20living%20area%20with%20a%20couch%2C%20a%20small%20closet%2C%20and%20a%20red%20door.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f7e7de1ba468a96ac0e8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20Corippo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo's%20family%20hoped%20to%20eventually%20rent%20out%20the%20primary%20residence%20on%20the%20pr