20a%20conspicuous%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20wishes%20she%20had%20thought%20about%20her%20curb%20appeal%20earlier%20in%20the%20building%20process%2C%20but%20her%20mom%20is%20helping%20her%20get%20her%20garden%20started%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECorippo%20doesn't%20see%20herself%20leaving%20her%20ADU%20anytime%20soon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blond%20woman%20smiles%20and%20looks%20down%20with%20trees%20behind%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f7d60a645d118818956d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMia%20Corippo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo%20has%20visions%20of%20renting%20out%20the%20ADU%20someday%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20she%20is%20loving%20living%20with%20her%20sister%20and%20being%20so%20close%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20I'm%20single%20and%20have%20no%20kids%2C%20I'll%20probably%20stay%20in%20that%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Corippo%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20again%2C%20that%20house%20could%20easily%20house%20a%20kid%20someday.%20It's%20got%20two%20bedrooms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorippo%20recommends%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-homeowner-earns-rental-incomes-tiny-homes-backyard-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eembracing%20ADU%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20buying%20a%20traditional%20home%20for%20people%20who%20have%20the%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20have%20the%20means%20to%20build%20on%20family%20land%2C%20I%20definitely%20would%20say%20take%20the%20chance%20and%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20live%20in%20that%20house%20or%20that%20ADU%20for%20a%20few%20years%20or%20a%20year%2C%20it's%20still%20going%20to%20put%20you%20ahead%20because%20you're%20spending%20so%20much%20less%20instead%20of%20buying%20in%20the%20crazy%20housing%20market.%26quot%3B%