om-wagner-to-intelligence-service-svr-how-russia-rewired-its-africa-operations%2Farticleshow%2F128643002.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%2039%20but%20just%20started%20contributing%20to%20a%20401(k)%20account.%20I%20have%20what%20I%20call%20'retirement%20planning%20paralysis.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Emily%20Achler%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6995fe79e1ba468a96ac3cd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20has%20always%20struggled%20to%20plan%20for%20retirement.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Emily%20Achler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20my%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20live%20in%20the%20present%20and%20ignored%20retirement%20planning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20about%20to%20turn%2040%2C%20I've%20started%20contributing%20to%20a%20401(k)%2C%20but%20I'm%20behind.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20still%20have%20to%20combine%20my%20past%20retirement%20accounts%2C%20but%20I'm%20fighting%20retirement%20planning%20paralysis.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%2039%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20haphazard%2C%20chaotic%2C%20and%20borderline%20nonexistent.%20I%20feel%20a%20lot%20of%20shame%20around%20this%20fact%20because%20I%20should%20know%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20job%20out%20of%20college%20was%20at%20PBS%2C%20where%20I%20opened%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Feverbank-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETIAA%20retirement%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%2022.%20Somewhere%20in%20the%20intervening%2018%20years%2C%20the%20retirement%20accounts%20at%20PBS%20switched%20from%20TIAA%20to%20Fidelity.%20I%20now%20get%20notifications%20from%20both%2C%20and%20it's%20confusing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20PBS%2C%20I%20worked%20for%20a%20public%20relations%20agency%20that%20most%20certainly%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fsafe-harbor-401k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E401(k)%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20absolutely%20didn't%20sign%20up%20for%20it.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20Redbox%2C%20where%20I%20again%20didn't%20enroll%20in%20a%20retirement%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20twisty-turny%20career%20path%2C%20including%20a%20pandemic-era%20six-year%20stint%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-founders-raising-millions-for-their-ai-startups-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estartup%20founder%3C%2Fa%3E%20developing%20a%20new%20tech%20product%20for%20book%20lovers.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20I%20worried%20about%20money%20every%20day%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20saving%20anything%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20that%20leaves%20me%20with%20a%20string%20of%20sparse%2C%20underfunded%20retirement%20accounts%2C%20regrets%20about%20the%20past%2C%20and%20worries%20about%20the%20future.%20I'm%20deep%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3Bretirement%20planning%20paralysis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202d6776c-76ad-4235-acc8-01bfc71f0792%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetirement%20wasn't%20on%20my%20radar%20for%20the%20bulk%20of%20my%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20shied%20away%20from%20retirement%20planning%20throughout%20my%20career%20for%20the%20same%20reason%20I%20didn't%20freeze%20my%20eggs%20or%20plan%20for%20any%20aspect%20of%20the%20future%3A%20Today%20is%20the%20only%20day%20that%20is%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20tried%20to%20live%20in%20the%20present%20because%20it%20feels%20presumptuous%20to%20plan%20the%20future.%20And%20the%20future%20always%20felt%20very%20far%20away%2C%20so%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20put%20planning%20off%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20in%20my%2020s%20and%2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20with%2040%20looming%2C%20I%20still%20feel%20uncertain%20about%20the%20future%2C%20but%20I%20also%20see%20my%20past%20avoidant%20behaviors%20as%20ones%20riddled%20with%20excuses%20and%20justifications.%20I%20suddenly%20realized%3A%20Just%20because%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20things%20will%20turn%20out%20doesn't%20mean%20I%20can't%20plan%20for%20future%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ab41a16-8bfb-49cd-8b7c-ff71cf4bc2ff%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20finally%20started%20saving%20for%20retirement%2C%20but%20still%20paralyzed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20I'm%20working%20full%20time%20at%20a%20B2B%20PR%20agency%2C%20and%20I'm%20finally%20maxing%20out%20my%20401(k).%20I've%20now%20doubled%20my%20total%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-retirement-savings-wealth-ai-abundance-personal-finance-experts-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20my%20previous%2015%2B%20years%20of%20corporate%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20still%20have%20at%20least%20two%2C%20maybe%20three%2C%20different%20retirement%20accounts.%20I%20know%20I%20should%20combine%20them%20all%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20to%20start%20or%20the%20best%20way%20to%20go%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20know%20that%20401(k)s%20can%20be%20rolled%20over%20or%20rolled%20up%2C%20so%20I%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20get%20this%20ball%20rolling%2C%20but%20I'm%20still%20struggling%20to%20find%20the%20motivation.%20It%20feels%20like%20total%20planning%20paralysis.%20This%20is%20my%20next%20big%20hurdle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f195200c-9875-4e67-88fd-cd5811dc215c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20feel%20about%20my%20future%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOptimistically%2C%20I%20would%20love%20to%20be%20in%20my%20late%2060s%20and%20retired.%20I%20w