5101-4303-beb5-fc75bc92b8c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Year%20of%20the%20Fire%20Horse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20dozen%20or%20so%20friends%20clamoured%20around%20my%20fireplace's%20mantel%20to%20grab%20their%20Dollar%20Store-bought%20journals%20and%20select%20a%20fancy%20gel%20pen.%20A%20ChatGPT-designed%20workshop%20on%20creating%20a%202026%20vision%20for%20one's%20life%20was%20about%20to%20begin%2C%20and%20two%20of%20my%20friends%20were%20fighting%20over%20who%20would%20get%20the%20last%20brown%20leather-bound%20journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20little%20before%20Lunar%20New%20Year%2C%20a%20holiday%20rooted%20in%20honoring%20the%20past%20while%20setting%20intentions%20for%20the%20future.%20And%20this%20year%2C%20instead%20of%20enjoying%20fireworks%20and%20celebrations%2C%20I%20hosted%20something%20much%20quieter.%20I%20invited%20my%20circle%20into%20my%20home%20to%20answer%20several%20journal%20prompts%20around%20career%2C%20love%2C%20fitness%2C%20and%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20January%201%20comes%20with%20too%20much%20pressure%3B%20you%20may%20remember%20me%20writing%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-working-during-holidays-recharge-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20intentionally%20slow%20start%20to%20the%20New%20Year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Lunar%20New%20Year%2C%20however%2C%20gifted%20me%20a%20second%20chance%20at%20intention.%20And%20what%20resulted%20around%20my%20dining%20room%20table%20was%20the%20perfect%20anecdote%20to%20help%20me%20game-plan%20my%20goals.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20party%2C%20we%20walked%20away%20with%20clarity%20and%20focus%2C%20and%20identified%20the%20gaps%20standing%20in%20our%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20recreate%20this%20moment%2C%20here%20are%20three%20tips%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20designed%20for%20reflection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EFirst%20things%20first%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ehere%20was%20my%20prompt%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einto%20ChatGPT%3A%20What%20are%20some%20good%20prompts%20for%20self-reflection%3F%20I%20want%20to%20create%20a%20vision%20workshop%20that%20sets%20goals%20on%20faith%2C%20finances%2C%20work%2C%20love%2C%20family%2C%20and%20life.%20Can%20you%20create%20the%20interactive%20workshop%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%3Cli%3EThen%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Ewe%20laid%20ground%20rules%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Yes%2C%20I%20encouraged%20my%20friends%20to%20share%20the%20goals%20they%20had%20scribbled%20down%2C%20but%20I%20also%20encouraged%20them%20to%20keep%20some%20answers%20close%20to%20the%20vest%2C%20as%20some%20goals%20thrive%20in%20incubation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELastly%2C%20I%20prioritized%20making%20my%20friends%20feel%20%3Cstrong%3Ecomfortable%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20There%20were%20candles%20lit%20everywhere%2C%20a%20basket%20of%20cheap%20yet%20cozy%20socks%20so%20they%20could%20kick%20their%20shoes%20off%20and%20relax%2C%20and%20don't%20forget%20the%20fancy%20gel%20pens%20to%20make%20the%20journaling%20experience%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhimsy-trend-explained-why-it-works-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20whimsical%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EI%20still%20don't%20know%20what%202026%20will%20bring%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20creating%20rushed%2C%20vague%20resolutions%2C%20at%20least%20I%20had%20a%20moment%20to%20be%20reminded%20that%20life%20moves%20in%20cycles%2C%20and%20ambition%20requires%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-lunar-new-year-vision-workshop-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771673701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998c027156648bc16a8a036%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-saturday-newsletter-lunar-new-year-vision-workshop-2026-2%22%2C