ff-ramp%2C%20a%20distraction%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flimits-large-language-models-chatgpt-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-openai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20dead%20end%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanke%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20applied%20economics%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20University%2C%20said%20he's%20%26quot%3Bon%20LeCun's%20side%20of%20the%20court%26quot%3B%20and%20considers%20AI%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Boverhyped%20and%20potentially%20dangerous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20October%20that%20whether%20the%20market's%20exuberance%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20rational%20or%20irrational%20would%20%26quot%3Blargely%20depend%20on%20whether%20the%20AI%20firms'%20spectacular%20revenue%20forecasts%20hold%20water.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20be%20wise%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-hanke-ai-boom-dotcom-bubble-tech-stocks-growth-forecasts-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuckle%20your%20seat%20belt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHanke%20was%20the%20president%20of%20Toronto%20Trust%20Argentina%20when%20it%20was%20the%20world's%20best-performing%20market%20mutual%20fund%20in%201995.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20an%20economic%20advisor%20to%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f313e93f-e674-4d04-97be-652f68b3575f%5C%22%3EBelievers%20and%20skeptics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20recent%20jitters%2C%20the%20AI%20boom%20seems%20to%20be%20going%20strong%20with%20OpenAI%20reportedly%20close%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-profitability-analyst-investor-opinions-funding-ipo-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraising%20north%20of%20%24100%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20potential%20%24850%20billion%20valuation.%20ChatGPT's%20maker%20crossed%20%2420%20billion%20in%20annualized%20revenue%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ET