insider.com%2Fstudent-turned-down-nyu-debt-free-community-college-path-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20media%20studies%20and%20a%20minor%20in%20the%20entertainment%20business.%20Throughout%20college%2C%20I%20held%20multiple%20internships%20in%20political%20campaigns%20and%20magazines%2C%20was%20active%20on%20my%20school's%20newspaper%2C%20networked%2C%20did%20well%20in%20my%20classes%2C%20and%20learned%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENYU%20was%20my%20dream%20school%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20my%20experience%20turned%20out%20exactly%20how%20I%20thought%20it%20would.%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbartending-to-business-owner-one-man-3-million-success-story-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20living%20my%20dream%20life%3A%20spending%20late%20nights%20with%20my%20best%20friends%2C%20exploring%20the%20entertainment%20scene%2C%20discovering%20new%20restaurants%20and%20bars%2C%20and%20taking%20advantage%20of%20every%20park%20the%20city%20had%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20couldn't%20land%20a%20job%20after%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20my%20dreams%20behind%20and%20move%20back%20home%20with%20my%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225fb8f6b-4f1d-46d7-a8ac-0174f073bd2a%5C%22%3EI%20couldn't%20afford%20New%20York%20without%20a%20full-time%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20felt%20inspired%20and%20hopeful%20in%20New%20York%2C%20like%20I%20finally%20arrived%20somewhere%20that%20matched%20the%20energy%20I%20had%20always%20carried%20inside%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20everything%20I%20could%20to%20stay.%20I%20applied%20to%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-gen-z-entry-level-job-market-shift-economy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20my%20last%20semester%20of%20college%20and%20the%20summer%20after%20graduation.%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20journalism%2C%20so%20I%20mostly%20applied%20for%20entry-level%20reporting%20and%20copyediting%20jobs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20marketing%20and%20social%20media%20management%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20score%20some%20interviews%2C%20but%20none%20turned%20into%20full-time%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20lease%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-living-in-tiny-apartment-in-nyc-microstudio-photos-2022%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEast%20Village%20apartment%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20in%20July%2C%20I%20faced%20a%20hard%20truth%3A%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20stay.%20I%20also%20didn't%20want%20to%20ask%20my%20parents%20for%20more%20financial%20help%2C%20knowing%20how%20much%20they%20had%20already%20supported%20me%20through%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20have%20a%20part-time%20job%20mentoring%20high%20school%20seniors%20through%20their%20college%20applications%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20enough%20to%20sustain%20living%20in%20New%20York%20while%20I%20tried%20to%20find%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20and%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20long%20it%20would%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cefd1c88-7ee6-46e2-956a-eeb42e96691f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20home%20to%20California%20was%20tough%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20all%20bad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20Santa%20Clarita%2C%20Calif.%2C%20about%2032%20miles%20north%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-things-about-living-in-los-angeles-residents-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20safe%2C%20quiet%20suburb%20where%20the%20pace%20of%20life%20is%20much%20slower%20than%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20after%20living%20in%20New%20York%20was%20a%20serious%20whiplash.%20My%20childhood%20bedroom%20suddenly%20felt%20smaller%20and%20quieter%2C%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20my%20college%20friends%20made%20the%20town%20feel%20emptier%20than%20I%20remembered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221089%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20author%20in%20her%20college%20graduation%20gown%20under%20a%20sign%20that%20reads%20new%20york%20university%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69978c26a645d1188189a3f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20had%20to%20move%20back%20home%20after%20NYU.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Diana%20Solis%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20parts%20I%20am%20grateful%20for%2C%20though.%20After%20almost%20four%20years%20of%20seeing%20them%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I%20finally%20get%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20parents.%20I%20also%20hated%20the%20harsh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuge-winter-storm-east-coast-heavy-snow-travel-delays-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEast%20Coast%20winters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20definitely%20do%20not%20miss%20schlepping%20my%20Trader%20Joe's%20groceries%20down%2010%20blocks%20and%20then%20up%20four%20flights%20of%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20here%20is%20gentler%2C%20the%20streets%20are%20quieter%2C%20and%20while%20it's%20not%20Manhattan%2C%20it's%20given%20me%20a%20space%20to%20breathe%20and%20reflect%20in%20ways%20I%20couldn't%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVisiting%20New%20York%20every%20few%20months%20reminds%20me%20why%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20city%2C%20but%20living%20at%20home%20has%20also%20shown%20me%20that%20slowing%20down%20is%20not%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20standing%20still.%20I've%20been%20creative%20with%20my%20career%2C%20focusing%20on%20writing%2C%20networking%2C%20and%20mentoring%2C%20while%20appreciating%20the%20small%20moments%20I%20took%20for%20granted%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c96610d-083b-4b76-8ccc-00a6d3ea32ed%5C%22%3EI'm%20still%20learning%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sometimes%20catch%20myself%20wondering%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20did%20this%20differently%2C%20would%20I%20be%20living%20and%20working%20in%20New%20York%20by%20now%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20constantly%20remind%20myself%20that%20I%20am%20only%2023%20and%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20to%20live.%20New%20York%20will%20always%20be%20there.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20times%20when%20I%20doubted%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-college-graduate-still-job-hunting-finding-self-outside-work-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20in%20journalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20considered%20quitting%2C%20but%20I%20love%20writing%2C%20and%20I%20have%20never%20been%20the%20type%20to%20give%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20still%20looking%20for%20a%20full-time%20writing%20job%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20I'm%20learning%20not%20to%20let%20it%20define%20my%20entire%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20such%20a%20strong%20believer%20that%20life%20happens%20for%20a%20reason.%20Maybe%20living%20in%20Santa%20Clarita%20again%20is%20teaching%20me%20lessons%20I%20need%20before%20I%20return%20to%20the%20city%20I%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiz%20Lindain%20is%20a%20freelance%20entertainment%20journalist%20based%20in%20Southern%20California.%20Connect%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fliz-allison-lindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Flizlindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flizlindain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyu-grad-couldnt-afford-new-york-city-