2ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnclt-clears-withdrawal-of-insolvency-proceedings-against-mahagun-126022100512_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20tariff%20loss%20could%20be%20a%20win%20for%20watch%20collectors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224727%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rolex%20watches%20on%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998ae79efb52c8bd0de935a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222973%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20watch%20dealer%20predicts%20that%20prices%20on%20the%20pre-owned%20market%20will%20drop%202%25%20to%203%25.%3Cp%3ETIMOTHY%20A.%20CLARY%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20on%20Friday%20to%20strike%20down%20most%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20decision%20made%20waves%20in%20the%20Swiss%20watch-collecting%20community.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESwitzerland%20has%20faced%20ups%20and%20downs%20as%20it%20has%20dealt%20with%20tariffs%20doled%20out%20by%20Trump.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%20world%20breathed%20a%20collective%20sigh%20of%20relief%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20decision%20on%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20trade%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%206-3%20decision%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20court%20ruled%20that%20imposing%20most%20of%20Trump's%20tariffs%20exceeded%20his%20authority%20under%20a%201970s%20law.%20The%20ruling%20is%20a%20hefty%20blow%20to%20the%20policies%20he%20put%20in%20place%20against%20foreign%20countries%2C%20which%20companies%20have%20had%20to%20reckon%20with%20for%20nearly%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWatch%20dealers%20have%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they%20and%20their%20shoppers%20stand%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20ruling.%20Pre-owned%20watch%20retailer%20SwissWatchExpo%20CEO%20Eugene%20Tutunikov%20said%20it%20would%20likely%20lead%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpre-owned-watch-sales-bobs-watches-increase-as-tariffs-loom-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20pre-owned%20watch%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months%20%E2%80%94%20he%20expects%20declines%20of%202%25%20to%203%25.%20Without%20tariffs%20looming%20overhead%2C%20the%20market%20is%20poised%20to%20snap%20back%20faster%20than%20retail%20prices%20as%20sellers%20set%20their%20prices%20and%20buyers%20take%20the%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSupply%20will%20loosen%20up%2C%20and%20purchasing%20power%20goes%20right%20back%20to%20the%20collector%20where%20it%20belongs%2C%26quot%3B%20Tutunikov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20break%20from%20tariffs%20would%20make%20the%20entry%20point%20for%20luxury%20watch%20collecting%20more%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECue%20the%20celebrations%20among%20Swiss%20watch%20lovers%20who've%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20storm%20of%20retail%20price%20increases%20from%20leading%20brands%20like%20Rolex%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Supply%20chain%20constraints%20also%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20do%20business%20in%20the%20secondhand%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-models-drove-pre-owned-watch-sales-as-tariffs-loomed-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETariff%20tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Switzerland%20and%20the%20US%20have%20been%20up%20and%20down%20since%20Trump's%20Liberation%20Day.%20US%20imports%20of%20Swiss%20goods%20faced%20a%20baseline%20tariff%20of%2010%25%20from%20April%202025%20until%20Trump%20eventually%20raised%20it%20to%2039%25%2C%20sending%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20watch%20industry.%20The%20two%20countries%20continued%20negotiations%20until%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20lower%20the%20rate%20to%2015%25%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-says-agreed-lower-tariffs-swiss-imports-rolex-davos-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espeaking%20with%20Rolex%20and%20other%20Swiss%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-reaction-supreme-court-scotus-tariff-ruling-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclapped%20back%20at%20the%20nation's%20highest%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20its%20Friday%20ruling%2C%20saying%20he'd%20find%20alternative%20ways%20to%20keep%20his%20trade%20agenda%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20did%20not%20overrule%20tariffs.%20They%20merely%20overruled%20a%20particular%20use%20of%20IEPPA%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20law%20referenced%20in%20the%20court's%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20move%20is%20still%20a%20win%20in%20the%20books%20of%20watch%20dealers%20who've%20said%20the%20decision%20would%20allow%20pricing%20in%20the%20pre-owned%20market%20to%20return%20to%20being%20based%20on%20value%20and%20demand%20rather%20than%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20are%20indeed%20lifted%2C%20we%20expect%20it%20would%20meaningfully%20improve%20sentiment%20across%20the%20industry%2C%20increase%20access%20to%20important%20pieces%2C%20and%20ultimately%20benefit%20collectors%2C%20retailers%2C%20and%20brands%20alike%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joshua%20Ganjei%2C%20CEO%20of%20European%20Watch%20Company%2C%20which%20sells%20pre-owned%20and%20vintage%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-collectors-could-gain-from-trumps-tariff-loss-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771671481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6998aebeefb52c8bd0de9367%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatch-collectors-could-gain-from-trumps-tariff-loss-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20watch%20world%20is%20rejoicing%20over%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20ruling%20on%20Trump's%20tariffs%20as%20dealers%20sa