sinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-healthy-fat-tips-robert-f-kennedy-new-guidelines-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enutrient-dense%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20vegetables%20and%20fish%20into%20your%20diet%20before%20taking%20pills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-an-exercise-routine-that-actually-works-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espend%20this%20money%20on%20a%20gym%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20you%20thought%20would%20get%20you%20moving%2C%20I%20would%20rather%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Chin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cdd968a-6260-4f5f-94dd-b1e6de893a3f%5C%22%3EThe%20ultimate%20question%3A%20what%20goes%20in%20your%20stack%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20perk%2C%20Thorne%20workers%20get%20to%20take%20home%20the%20supplements%20they%20make%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20monthly%20allotment%20of%20products%2C%20free%20of%20charge.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20this%20is%20great%20quality%20control.%20Amy%20Caplette%2C%20Thorne's%20SVP%20of%20Quality%20%26amp%3B%20Regulatory%20Affairs%2C%20told%20me%20that%20if%20it's%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20serve%20your%20family%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20coming%20off%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20suggesting%20a%20standard%20'stack%2C'%20we%20encourage%20employees%20to%20make%20informed%20choices%20based%20on%20their%20own%20goals%2C%20lifestyles%2C%20and%20health%20considerations%2C%20with%20expert%20support%20available%20when%20helpful%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20after%20our%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoctors%20say%20that%20while%20that's%20probably%20not%20an%20unsafe%20strategy%2C%20it's%20not%20exactly%20optimal%20in%20a%20sector%20where%20influencers%20are%20often%20the%20loudest%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20always%20comes%20back%20to%20the%20influencers%20and%20these%20certain%20celebrity%20doctors%20saying%20that%20traditional%20medicine%20has%20abandoned%20you.%20We%20have%20the%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohammed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20said%20he%20understands%20the%20impulse%20to%20boost.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturmeric-curcumin-health-benefits-anti-inflammatory-antioxidant-2018-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethrows%20a%20little%20turmeric%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20morning%20coffee%2C%20thinking%20of%20it%20as%20a%20mild%20anti-inflammatory.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultivitamins-for-memory-older-adults-benefit-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epops%20a%20multivitamin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hoping%20to%20refill%20any%20dietary%20deficiencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20the%20factory%20with%20some%20creatine%20samples%2C%20plus%20a%20berry-flavored%20amino%20acid%20powder%2C%20and%20electrolyte%20packets.%20The%20electrolytes%20were%20delicious%2C%20and%20I%20quickly%20reached%20for%20them%20on%20hot%2C%20busy%20days%20when%20I%20felt%20my%20hydration%20lagging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20other%20supplements%20have%20been%20sitting%20in%20the%20kitchen%20pantry%20ever%20since.%20Do%20I%20really%20%3Cem%3Eneed%3C%2Fem%3E%20them%3F%20Would%20daily%20creatine%20help%2C%20or%20would%20it%20just%20make%20my%20muscles%20a%20little%20rounder%3F%20It%20all%20feels%20so%20marginal.%20For%20now%2C%20I'll%20stick%20to%20working%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthorne-supplement-factory-charleston-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771671301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69976f9de1ba468a96ac56ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthorne-supplement-factory-charleston-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20visited%20Thorne's%20supplement%20factory%20where%20creatine%2C%20electrolytes%2C%20and%20magnesium%20were%20